	(506,301,'FIT FI01','Fit is not a chair, Fit is not an easy chair, Fit can best be described as a seating net. A novel ergonomic object that does not necessarily look like something you can sit in at first glance; the typical horizontal seat is missing, which will probably surprise the viewer at fi rst. Some people may think, how does that work? And: can it work at all? When not in use, Fit is a flat object with a net fabric stretched over the entire frame. It is divided into intelligent flexible and supporting zones. The bulge only appears when you sit down.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,2548),
	(507,301,'Proseidia: Younico 2406','The younico is a professional chair concept; an optimized synchronous mechanism complemented with excellent seat tilt and seat depth adjustment. Younico Pro is in the material design\nwith the best in the construction business.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,24586),
